OL,6,F"Now getting a projection of my next
OL,7,Fdirect debt being nearly double what
OL,8,Fit is now - from #343 to #675 a month
OL,9,F- is terrifying.
OL,11,F"I keep thinking I won't be able to
OL,12,Fpay the rent, we are going to lose our
OL,13,Fhome, where are we going to live? This
OL,14,Fis our home, we've been here for 15
OL,15,Fyears."
