OL,3,CMum fears 'terrifying' energy cost of
OL,4,Ckeeping disabled son alive
OL,6,FThe new energy price cap comes into
OL,7,Fforce on 1 October. It sets the
OL,8,Fmaximum amount energy suppliers can
OL,9,Fcharge for each unit of energy and
OL,10,Fstanding charge on a standard variable
OL,11,Ftariff.
OL,13,F'I'm so afriad'
OL,15,FAs well as his ventilator, Lewis
OL,16,Frelies on a range of equipment,
OL,17,Fincluding a humidifier and a sats
OL,18,Fmonitor which run constantly.
