OL,3,CMum fears 'terrifying' energy cost of
OL,4,Ckeeping disabled son alive
OL,6,FThere are also suction machines,
OL,7,Ffeeding pumps, hoists, and a pressure
OL,8,Fsore mattress.
OL,10,FMs Tolmie said the machines cannot be
OL,11,Fswitched off and many have back-ups
OL,12,Fwhich also need to remain charged.
OL,14,FShe said: "It's so difficult because
OL,15,Fwe are so grateful that our family
OL,16,Fmember is here and at home. But at the
OL,17,Fsame time don't leave us in a position
OL,18,Fwhere we are struggling to keep them
OL,19,Falive at home because we can't afford
OL,20,Fit.
