OL,4,Ckeeping disabled son alive
OL,6,FA government spokesperson said
OL,7,Fministers "recognise the challenges
OL,8,Ffamilies, including those with
OL,9,Fdisabilities, are facing with their
OL,10,Fenergy bills".
OL,12,FThey added: "We are working closely
OL,13,Fwith suppliers to ensure vulnerable
OL,14,Fhouseholds are supported this winter
OL,15,Fand the #150 Warm Home Discount will
OL,16,Fhelp around three million eligible low-
OL,17,Fincome households with their energy
OL,18,Fbills."
